Add the following line to powershell profile (notepad $PROFILE):

. $pathToMyEnv\profile.ps1

where $pathToMyEnv is path to you clone of MyEnv

ConEmu task example:

*powershell.exe
    -new_console:P:"^<ConEmu^>"
    -NoExit
    -NoProfile
    -Command "
        Set-Item -Path "Env:CmdEnvFilePath" -Value A:\repos\ols1\tools\path1st\myenv.cmd;
        . A:\repos\myenv\profile.ps1;
        Push-Location $env:SrcRoot;"